narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: 130 is definitely a lot more chill than 120. You spend most of your classtime going over things you're supposed to read from the course packet and learning very little new grammar. I would definitely recommend taking 130 with Oscar if you can. He wants you to learn, but he doesn't expect your whole life to be español, so if you miss a homework assignment every now and then or can't form a question in Spanish and have to use English, it's not a huge deal.
Take it with Oscar. He's fun, nice, and a great teacher.
